\c 17
\s Jobho anokumbira kuti Mwari amururamisire
\p
\v 1 Mweya wangu waparara; mazuva angu adzimwa\x + 18.5,6.\x*; makuva ndeangu\x + Map. 88.3,4.\x*.
\v 2 Vaseki havapo pamwe neni here? Neziso rangu rinogara mukumukira kwavo.
\v 3 Zvino isai rubatso rwangu kwamuri\x + Isa. 38.14. Map. 119.122. VaHeb. 7.22.\x*; ndiani uyo acharova paruoko rwangu\x + Zvir. 6.1.\x*?
\v 4 Nokuti moyo yavo yakavanzwa pakunzwisisa; naizvozvo hamungavakwiridziri.
\v 5 Anotaurira shamwari dzake nekuda kwemubairo, nemeso evana vake achapera\x + 11.20.\x*.
\v 6 Zvino wakandimisa ndive tsumo yerudzi\x + 30.9. Map. 44.14. 69.11. Det. 28.37. Jow. 2.17.\x*, kusvika ndava wakasvisvinwa pamberi parwo.
\v 7 Uye ziso rangu rodzedzerera nekuda kwekutambudzika\x + Map. 6.7.\x*, nemitezo yangu yose yava semumvuri\x + 14.2.\x*.
\v 8 Vakarurama vachavhunduswa nazvo\x + Isa. 52.14.\x*, neasine mhosva achamukira asingadi Mwari\x + 31.29.\x*.
\v 9 Zvino wakarurama achabatirira panzira yake, newakachena pamaoko achawedzera simba\x + 22.30. Map. 24.4.\x*.
\v 10 Asi imwi mese, dzokai, muuye ikozvino; nokuti handingawani wakachenjera pakati penyu\x + 6.29.\x*.
\p
\v 11 Mazuva angu apfuura\x + 7.6. 9.25.\x*; vavariro dzangu dzadambuka\x + 18.14.\x*, iyo fuma yemoyo wangu.
\v 12 Vanomisa usiku huve masikati\x + Isa. 5.20.\x*; chiedza chiri pedo\x + 7.4.\x* pamberi perima\x + 23.17.\x*.
\v 13 Kana ndichirinda, guva richava imba yangu\x + Mup. 12.5.\x*; ndawaridza mubhedha wangu murima.
\v 14 Ndakadana kuguva \add ndichiti\add*: Iwe uri baba vangu; kuhonye: Mai vangu nehanzvadzi yangu.
\v 15 Zvino ikozvino tariro yangu iripi? Haiwa tariro yangu, ndiani achaiona?
\v 16 Zvichaburukira kumazariro\x + 18.13.\x* eguva, patichazorora\x + 3.17,18,19.\x*\x + 36.16.\x* pamwe muvhu\x + 21.26. 40.13.\x*.